These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
Beverage: cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
Pet: fish, dog, goat, horse
1. Beverage:hot-chocolate is between Beverage:cola and Pet:dog##2
2. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left or right of Pet:fish##3
3. Beverage:hot-chocolate is somewhere between Beverage:tea and Beverage:cola##7
4. Pet:dog is in an even position##4
5. Beverage:tea is on the right of Pet:goat##1
6. Pet:dog is somewhere to the left of Pet:fish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | tea       | hot-chocolate | cola        |
| Pet      | goat  | dog | horse        | fish |

