2. Pet:snake is somewhere to the left of Pet:dog##5
3. Pet:snake is somewhere to the right of Color:chestnut##5
4. Pet:goat is on the left of Pet:snake##1
5. Color:chestnut is between Color:yellow and Color:lilac##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | hedgehog | goat       | snake         | dog     |
| Color   | lilac   | chestnut | yellow | fuchsia |

